---
//BLOQUE PROBLEMA APP

---

<div id="container">
  
    <div class="main">
        <div class="probl">
            <h2>Challenge</h2>
           <p class="parrafo">
            A sedentary lifestyle is one of the biggest problems we face today, but most solutions rely on the user’s willpower.
            Health apps often fail because they require active and consistent commitment.

            
           </p>
        </div>
        
                <div class="ideas">
                    
                            <div class="card">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <h3 class="card-title">ideas 💡</h3>  
                                    <p class="card-text">Design an experience where the content is the reward.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="card">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <h3 class="card-title">ideas 💡</h3>  
                                    <p class="card-text">The app lets you listen to audiobooks, but there's one catch:<br>
                                    👉 <strong>They only play when it detects that you're walking.</strong> </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="card">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <h3 class="card-title">ideas 💡</h3>  
                                    <p class="card-text">If you stop, the content pauses.
                                This makes the act of walking an essential part of the experience, rather than an extra chore.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
            
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

<style>

        #container{
            z-index: 3;
        }
    	.main{
           display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            flex-wrap: nowrap;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0 auto;
            z-index: 3;
           
            font-family: 'Inter';
           
            background-color: #7D92FF;
 
		
	}

    .probl{
        width: 50%;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 50px;
       
    }
    .ideas{
        width: 50%;
        padding: 100px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: row;
        flex-wrap: nowrap;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
    }

  
 
      
        .card {
            display: flex; 
            flex-direction: column; 
            border-radius: 16px  16px 16px 16px;
            width: 272px;
            height: 237px;
            box-shadow: 2px 7px 13px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            overflow: hidden; 
            
            border-color: #000000;
        }
        .card-body{
            background-color: #fffcfc;
            flex-grow: 1;
            padding: 24px; 
        }

        .card-title{
            color: #ffffff;
            text-shadow: 0px 0px 20px #7D92FF ; 
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 25px;
            margin: 0px; 
            padding: 0px; 
            text-align: center;
            
        }
        .card-text{
            line-height: 1.4;
            margin: 10px 0px 0px 0px; 
            font-size: 17px;
            color: #444;
            text-align: left;
            
            
        }


    h1{
        animation: fade 1s ease-in ;
        font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
        margin-top: -100px;
        font-weight: 700;
        opacity: 0.6;
        color: #FFFFFF; 
        text-shadow: 2px 2px 6px #1e0125;   
        }
    
    h2{
        animation: fade 1s ease-in ;
        font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
        
        font-weight: 700;
        opacity: 0.6;
        color: #FFFFFF; 
        text-shadow: 2px 2px 6px #1e0125;  
    }

    p{
        animation: fade 1s ease-in ;
        font-family: 'Inter';
        font-style: normal;
        font-weight: 400;
        font-size: 18px;
        text-align: left;
        letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        color: #FFFFFF; 
        line-height: 40px;
        
       
    }

    	@keyframes fade{
		0%{
			     opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(30px);
		}
		100%{
			     opacity: 0.6;
      transform: translateY(0);
		}
	}

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .main {
        height: auto;
        min-height: 100vh;
        padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    .probl {
        width: 100%;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1rem;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .ideas {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 1rem 0;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 1.25rem;
        
    }

    .card {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 340px;
        height: auto;
        
    }

    p {
        line-height: 28px;
        font-size: 16px;
       
    }
}
   
</style>